# NAME

schoolmesh\_sambaaccount\_create - Create a samba account for a user

# SYNOPSIS

schoolmesh\_sambaaccount\_create *username* *fullname* *password*

# DESCRIPTION

Use this script to create a posix account.
Some checks are done before the creation.

# EXAMPLES

	schoolmesh_sambaaccount_create john 'John Doe' ck33LmrdH_45

